						<summary>

						<p>Māsti stone set up in the Siddhēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Rāmachandrarāya A.D. 1288.</p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription, referring itself to the reign of Rāmachandra's regnal year 18, is dated in Sarvadhāri, Paushya su. 5, Wednesday corresponding to 1288 A.D. December 29.</p>						

						<p>This record mentions god Svayaṁbhū Tailēśvara of Hānuṁgal and seems to record the death of a person in a fight.</p>						

						</summary>
